== Configuration ==

=== Files ===

All configuration {{c|dhcpcd}} can be set in the {{Path|/etc/dhcpcd.conf}} file, but for most installations {{c|dhcpcd}} will work out of the box presuming most computers nowadays are behind a router or access point running a DHCP server. Though {{c|man 5 dhcpcd.conf}}<ref name=manpage>Roy Marples. [http://roy.marples.name/man/html5/dhcpcd.conf.html DHCPCD.CONF(5)], [http://roy.marples.name/blog/ Roy Marples's personal blog], March 9th, 2015. Retrieved on May 07th, 2015.</ref> will be helpful in case advanced configuration is required.

